<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nibblenotes - Your Digital Recipe Haven</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }

        .float-emoji {
            display: inline-block;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .highlight-text {
            transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .highlight-text:hover {
            color: #ff6b6b;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        #cta-button {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        #cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container my-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Welcome to Nibblenotes! <span class="float-emoji">🍴✨</span></h1>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                <p>Founded by Ashley and Bernard in sunny Stellenbosch, Cape Town in September 2024, Nibblenotes is your <span class="highlight-text">digital recipe haven</span>! <span class="float-emoji">🧑‍🍳📖</span></p>
                <p>Whether you're creating your own <span class="highlight-text">culinary masterpieces</span> <span class="float-emoji">🥘</span> or capturing favorite recipes from around the web <span class="float-emoji">🌐</span>, Nibblenotes helps you store and organize them with ease. Our platform makes it easy to save everything in one place!</p>
                <p>Need inspiration? Let our <span class="highlight-text">AI-powered chef</span> <span class="float-emoji">👩‍💻</span> whip up personalized recipes just for you! Save, share, and build your own custom recipebook <span class="float-emoji">📚</span>—all in one fun platform.</p>
                <p>From simple snacks <span class="float-emoji">🍪</span> to gourmet meals <span class="float-emoji">🍲</span>, we're here to make cooking creative, easy, and fun for everyone. <span class="float-emoji">🧡</span></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <h3 class="mb-4 highlight-text">Ready to get cooking?</h3>

            <button id="cta-button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Sign up and start your own recipebook today! <span class="float-emoji">🎉👩‍🍳</span></button>

</body>
</html>
